    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# document models have 37 available operations across 7 categories\n\nThe document model document type (`powerhouse/document-model`) supports 37 operations:\n\n| Category | Operations | Count |\n|----------|-----------|-------|\n| Header Management | SET_MODEL_NAME, SET_MODEL_ID, SET_MODEL_EXTENSION, SET_MODEL_DESCRIPTION, SET_AUTHOR_NAME, SET_AUTHOR_WEBSITE | 6 |\n| Module Management | ADD_MODULE, SET_MODULE_NAME, SET_MODULE_DESCRIPTION, DELETE_MODULE, REORDER_MODULES | 5 |\n| Operation Management | ADD_OPERATION, SET_OPERATION_NAME, SET_OPERATION_SCHEMA, SET_OPERATION_DESCRIPTION, SET_OPERATION_TEMPLATE, SET_OPERATION_REDUCER, MOVE_OPERATION, DELETE_OPERATION, REORDER_MODULE_OPERATIONS | 9 |\n| Error Management | ADD_OPERATION_ERROR, SET_OPERATION_ERROR_CODE, SET_OPERATION_ERROR_NAME, SET_OPERATION_ERROR_DESCRIPTION, SET_OPERATION_ERROR_TEMPLATE, DELETE_OPERATION_ERROR, REORDER_OPERATION_ERRORS | 7 |\n| Example Management | ADD_OPERATION_EXAMPLE, UPDATE_OPERATION_EXAMPLE, DELETE_OPERATION_EXAMPLE, REORDER_OPERATION_EXAMPLES | 4 |\n| State Management | SET_STATE_SCHEMA, SET_INITIAL_STATE, ADD_STATE_EXAMPLE, UPDATE_STATE_EXAMPLE, DELETE_STATE_EXAMPLE, REORDER_STATE_EXAMPLES | 6 |\n| Versioning | \u26a0\ufe0f Not implemented | 0 |\n\nSince [[versioning operations on document models are not implemented]], the versioning category is unusable.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[schema design]]\n- [[mcp workflows]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:33.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:33.000Z"
    }
  },
